com.dropbox.core.v2.files

Class ThumbnailV2Error

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.v2.files.ThumbnailV2Error

  • public final class ThumbnailV2Error
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an open tagged union. Tagged unions instances are always associated to a specific tag. This means only one of the isAbc() methods will return true. You can use tag() to determine the tag associated with this instance.

    Open unions may be extended in the future with additional tags. If a new tag is introduced that this SDK does not recognized, the OTHER value will be used.

      • tag

        public ThumbnailV2Error.Tag tag()
        Returns the tag for this instance.

        This class is a tagged union. Tagged unions instances are always associated to a specific tag. This means only one of the isXyz() methods will return true. Callers are recommended to use the tag value in a switch statement to properly handle the different values for this ThumbnailV2Error.

        If a tag returned by the server is unrecognized by this SDK, the ThumbnailV2Error.Tag.OTHER value will be used.

        Returns:
        the tag for this instance.
